  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 31e2412c87638a942b571fad5d879d57, type: 3}
  m_Name: ClassroomLesson_ForcedPlayerMovement_FoR_Gentle
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ClassroomTitle: 
  LessonSteps:
  - m_DialogueString: "Welcome to the Classroom. \rYou have just experienced the
      first variant of Player Initiated Movement. \r"
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bfd070a869b6c3b4cbdd73c3d6de06ca, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: Forced Movement refers to the movement controls which users
      cannot initiate on their own.
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4bc0e11d3c7b93e419edc08f628c2a69, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: "This ensures that the player moves in a certain way and allow
      them to undergo a specific experience. \r"
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4bc0e11d3c7b93e419edc08f628c2a69, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: 'In this set up, it is designed for you to experience being
      moved around with a frame of reference where the map only has gentle corners. '
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 77043d57dfb7014449c5d05467cca466, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: The frame of the windshield of the car acts as a frame of reference,
      thus you are able to focus on it, instead of the surroundings that are moving
      past.
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 77043d57dfb7014449c5d05467cca466, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: With gentle corners, vection is reduced as your virtual environment
      moves less drastically compared to reality. This alleviates the effect of vection,
      reducing motion sickness.
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 77043d57dfb7014449c5d05467cca466, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: Next, you will ride through a slightly different map.
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6f13ccda2f65ea04c9ea4559772ef214, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: 'Whenever you are ready, head to the door on your left. '
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 0
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6f13ccda2f65ea04c9ea4559772ef214, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
